.projects
  .container
    .row
      .col-xl-12
        h3.projects__title what we do
      .col-xl-7.col-lg-6.col-md-5.pl-md-3.pr-md-3.col-12.pl-0.pr-0
        .projects__pictures
          img.projects__img(src="./img/projects/img1.png", alt="img")
      .col-xl-5.col-lg-6.col-md-7.col-12
        .projects__block.block.d-xl-flex.flex-xl-column
          h5.block__subtitle One World
          h3.block__title Trade Center
          p.block__article  Increasing prosperity in our lives can be accomplished by having the right frame of mind. The truth is, our thoughts are very powerful.
          .block__btn
            a.block__link(href="#") more details
          div.block__footer
            a(href="https://www.google.com/maps?q=new+york", target="_blank")
              i.fas.fa-map-marker-alt
              small.block__small New York City, United States - 1776 feet
      .col-xl-5.col-lg-6.col-md-7.order-md-1.col-12.order-2 
        .projects__block.block.d-xl-flex.flex-xl-column
          h5.block__subtitle International
          h3.block__title Commerce Centre
          p.block__article  Successful businesses have many things in common, today we’ll look at the big ‘R’ of recognition and how a digital advertising network may help.
          .block__btn
            a.block__link(href="#") more details
          div.block__footer
            a(href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/hong+kong/", target="_blank")
              i.fas.fa-map-marker-alt
              small.block__small Hong Kong - 1588 Feet
      .col-xl-7.col-lg-6.col-md-5.order-md-2.pl-md-3.pr-md-3.col-12.order-1.pl-0.pr-0
        .projects__pictures--right
          img.projects__img.projects__img--right(src="./img/projects/img2.png", alt="img")